 be the subject of a wider consultation\\\".\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The chairperson\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"the association Friends\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"the Champ de Mars\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"the park\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2963}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider consultation\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hidalgo had already announced her intention to retain some of the symbols of the Olympics, including the innovative cauldron placed in front of the Louvre museum, as well as statues used during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3204, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 0.9988299965363763, \"rank\": 0.0011713739753592132, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hidalgo\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"her intention\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"the symbols\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"the innovative cauldron\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3180}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"statues\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3237}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told the Ouest-France newspaper on Saturday she wanted to keep the rings and: \\\"the decision is up to me and I have the agreement of the IOC (International Olympic Committee)\\\".\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3413,